result.name: 回到味來雞煲火鍋私房菜

reviews.text:
An absolutely disappointing experience at this restaurant on a Friday night with my friends. I’ve been here for 5-6 times already and had always appreciated the quality of food every time. I made a booking again recently, not knowing the restaurant now only offers all-you-can-eat (or “semi-buffet”) and you can only eat for 2 hours. When I surprisingly realized the change when we settled down, I asked the waiter: “Do we really have to finish everything within 2 hours? I can order from the a-la-carte menu as usual so we can sit for a longer time” The waiter answered they only offer buffet menu now, but if no one is waiting for our table then maybe we can sit for awhile longer. 

This is why when the waiter asked us to settle the bill and leave in 15 mins we were so shocked and unprepared. It took them more than 15 mins to refill the chicken pot for us, and another 20 mins for the hotpot. If we were under the impression that we needed to leave within 2 hours we would have ordered the refill and everything else much earlier. It was ridiculous to ask us to finish everything within 15 mins. I would have appreciated if they at the very least reminded us 30 mins in advance. 

This restaurant is offering buffet, but their service couldn’t catch up with the speed that is expected of a buffet. What makes matters worse, the seafood was not fresh at all and the overall quality of food was disappointing. The buffet menu only offers 4 types of soup base but the 2 that we chose were far from flavorful. The quality was much much much better a few months ago but the price was more or less the same. 

I wouldn’t come back again.

海鮮新鮮，肉品不錯，單價不太高 $68 6支啤酒可做加點（其實cp值算高）
環境就不太優了，地板有點油油，穿細跟高跟鞋很怕跌倒。座位狹窄 椅背很直，廁所有點可怕。
以「任食」這個角度來看是可一試的，飲料多是罐裝，而且雖然有寫限2hr，但不會趕人，服務也算迅速有禮。

我們坐在窗邊位置，可以看到彌敦道街景。
準備吃辣的東西，要叫一些冰凍飲品幫助減低刺激。
不能吃太辣，只選小辣一隻雞。 這家的雞煲送上後多煮一分多鐘再翻炒一下便可以吃了。雞件肉質嫩滑鮮美， 加上微辣麻香醬汁，表嫂大讚好好味。
食完雞，店員送來粉絲蒸扇貝，不錯吃。我們的火鍋選了南瓜蜆湯底，湯內有些鮮蜆。
手切牛頸脊牛味濃郁，好味啊。海鮮也很新鮮，特別是鮮蝦，吃著鮮甜美味。雞子，味道和質感不是每個人都能接受的。
蔬菜好新鮮，味道也很清甜。豬肉和羊肉也好食， 肉味好鮮。

海鮮和手切牛頸脊肉不是任食， 客人可以追加任食表單上的火鍋配料。
雞煲最好吃， 兩百多一個人很抵噠。
食中只臭了的蜆✖X
道地的香港火鍋，雞煲先以香辛料炒過，吃起來有點類似三杯雞，但有點不一樣，將雞肉吃完之後，於鍋中注入高湯，立刻變成火鍋，將豬肉、牛肉、鹿肉與海鮮，放入湯中涮涮，湯鮮味美，與之前的感受又是不同層次，三五好友，來此聚餐聊天，互相交流，感覺真的很好，這裡離港鐵站近，公車也多，找個機會來此體驗港式火鍋。
